{"tid":325265,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聞賣盤扯火   黎智英：賣咗我一世變契弟","createTime":"2017-07-17T05:50:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-17T06:17:35.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"90d38dd363fe151a98c940e49fd5c410b8a503ef","tid":325265,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T05:50:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20130628/51514185/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20130628%2F51514185%2F&d=lPKRRz6ssMTRD7aqGbf%2B%2FRxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=1cdfb8bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20130628%2F51514185%2F&h=84c0fe29\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20130628/51514185/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">聞賣盤扯火<br />\n黎智英：賣咗我一世變契弟</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n外界盛傳壹傳媒及旗下刊物可能賣盤，壹傳媒主席黎智英早上出席電台節目時，直指有關傳聞是「亂噏」，又聲言：「賣咗我一世變契弟，點肯做呀，我而家又唔係冇錢。」他強調：「香港係我屋企，我有責任爭取民主同普選，呢個責任我冇得卸！」<br />\n<br />\n被問到為何一度想賣出台灣《蘋果日報》，黎智英直言因壹電視遲遲不獲發牌導致心灰意冷，「一個民主地方（台灣），可以攞個牌使咗30億、輸咗30億，都可以未有個牌畀我嘅」。<br />\n<br />\n談到傳媒行業未來發展方向，黎智英預計收費報紙會慢慢式微，但仍有生存空間，因為「好多人睇報紙唔會淨係睇張紙，係睇整個製造新聞嘅機構」。他又指，未來傳媒發展一定以手機平台為主導，因手機方便、亦佔人最多時間，「等人好、車上面好、去廁所好，都可以㩒一㩒、睇一睇」。<br />\n<br />\n黎智英又估計，十年後《蘋果》動新聞的點擊率，將由現時的每日三千萬，增至八、九千萬，甚至一億。<br />\n<br />\n至於旗下免費報章《爽報》未見起色，黎智英強調有信心幾個月內收支平衡，又指《爽報》繼續做下去可為集團的報紙市場留有發展空間。"},{"pid":"c75c08616b65ce7d39b2c217b0ee4b8e7b1aee55","tid":325265,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T05:50:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"389ed53411b2415eebee1de7cb38abb50dad7d7a","tid":325265,"uid":59976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T06:10:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3598/3585087315_52c980ab5d_o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffarm4.static.flickr.com%2F3598%2F3585087315_52c980ab5d_o.jpg&h=2280e371&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2400dc3f406327344e5d5ba84bb87cfa276e01ef","tid":325265,"uid":23180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T06:14:07.000Z","msg":"賣盤都啱嘅<br />\n<br />\n共匪已經做緊連Nazi都唔敢做嘅野<br />\n<br />\n呢幾年又銅鑼灣書店又盛咁<br />\n<br />\n遲D香港又割高鐵站行匪法連白牌車都唔洗出動<br />\n<br />\n死肥佬套現著草，有得自保就自保先都啱嘅"},{"pid":"2d061861ed88cda0caff7d85dbac32446a7d8218","tid":325265,"uid":56702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T06:15:56.000Z","msg":"契弟黎"},{"pid":"57fa8626b3650578d07443a2d0c6a85193bfca09","tid":325265,"uid":54721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T06:17:35.000Z","msg":"不嬲都契弟黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}